    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332660/extras/b870607801a2efd7b44366293c467f7b.avif?t=1735347943\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332660/extras_big/b870607801a2efd7b44366293c467f7b.avif?t=1735347943 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >is an innovative score-attack movement-shooter crafted from the design lessons of modern classics such as<i> ULTRAKILL</i> and<i> HYPER DEMON</i>. Featuring a simple player move-set in combination with synergistic enemy design, <i>SICKO SANCTUM 2</i> represents the cutting-edge of digitized violence. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ENEMIES ARE WEAPONS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332660/extras/0a32dd28cd75e84774d4fef0a20194d5.poster.avif?t=1735347943\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332660/extras/0a32dd28cd75e84774d4fef0a20194d5.webm?t=1735347943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332660/extras/0a32dd28cd75e84774d4fef0a20194d5.mp4?t=1735347943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Powerful special moves can be done through interacting with enemies in specific ways. Sometimes the strongest attacks are not your own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>STYLE IS POWER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332660/extras/d53c50fdf94f8f8fcb60edb482f3e218.poster.avif?t=1735347943\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332660/extras/d53c50fdf94f8f8fcb60edb482f3e218.webm?t=1735347943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332660/extras/d53c50fdf94f8f8fcb60edb482f3e218.mp4?t=1735347943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stylish play is rewarded with level ups that improve speed and damage. Creative moment to moment strategy is essential to survival. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>!?!?!?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332660/extras/8966b90b387431b43c03e1841a5316a7.poster.avif?t=1735347943\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332660/extras/8966b90b387431b43c03e1841a5316a7.webm?t=1735347943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332660/extras/8966b90b387431b43c03e1841a5316a7.mp4?t=1735347943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get to the core of a mysterious and surreal post-apocalyptic world. What's at the bottom and beyond? Only through violence may answers be found. </p>",
